// main.js

import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import 'bootstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import { router } from './router' // router'覺 fonksiyon olarak import et

createApp(App).use(router()).mount('#app') // router'覺 fonksiyon olarak kullan
